text: Sede do BankBoston is a skyscraper in São Paulo, Brazil. It is 145 meters (476 feet) tall and has 35 floors. It was built in 2002, and is a modern skyscraper of Brazil and Latin America. == Photo gallery == Image:Brooklin ¹².jpg == Other websites == *Emporis *SkyscraperPage Category:Skyscrapers in Brazil Category:Buildings and structures in São Paulo Category:2002 establishments in Brazil
